    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169040/extras/915f507c8fd1c5cdc097e601b59be113.avif?t=1734425756\" width=630 height=500 /></span><br><br>Welcome to &quot;<strong>Seeking Cat</strong>&quot;, a charming hidden object game where your mission is to find all the mischievous cats hiding in a cozy, cluttered room.<br><br>In this beautifully crafted, isometric environment, playful cats have tucked themselves away in the most unexpected places. With their tiny paws and curious eyes, these furry friends have found clever spots to hide among the room’s many items. Whether it’s a kitten peeking out from behind a stack of books, a cat curled up in a basket, or one perched high on a shelf, each feline is waiting to be found.<br><br>As you explore the room, you'll need to search every nook and cranny—from the bookshelf brimming with knick-knacks to the desk filled with gaming gear. The warm, inviting atmosphere and detailed design make every discovery delightful, as you uncover each cat's unique hiding spot.<br><br>Can you find all the cats and prove yourself as the ultimate cat finder in &quot;Seeking Cat&quot;?",
